{
 "_meta": {
  "npc": "Iolo",
  "batches": 2
 },
 "translations": [
  {
   "offset": 2,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "Iolo",
   "zh": "尤洛",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "NPC 名"
  },
  {
   "offset": 7,
   "len": 21,
   "en": "your old friend Iolo.",
   "zh": "汝舊識尤洛是也。",
   "zh_bytes": 16,
   "note": "DESC 句"
  },
  {
   "offset": 37,
   "len": 88,
   "en": "\"Well, $P, do you need @help with something? Or maybe you've got time for a @story, eh?\"",
   "zh": "「嗯，$P，可有事需在下相@help（助）？又或閣下尚有閒暇聽一則@story（故事）故事？」",
   "zh_bytes": 60,
   "note": "保留 $P"
  },
  {
   "offset": 135,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "name",
   "zh": "名字",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 140,
   "len": 76,
   "en": "\"Iolo's the only name I remember having.\" (He pronounces his name 'Yo-low.')",
   "zh": "「在下記憶所及，唯『尤洛』一名而已。」（他將名字唸作『Yo-low』。）",
   "zh_bytes": 66,
   "note": "保留發音註記"
  },
  {
   "offset": 222,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "help",
   "zh": "幫助",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 227,
   "len": 83,
   "en": "\"If you want me to @gather all our gold together so you can carry it, just say so.\"",
   "zh": "「若閣下欲令在下@gather（匯集）眾人之金幣交由閣下攜帶，但說無妨。」",
   "zh_bytes": 57,
   "note": "@gather→@匯集"
  },
  {
   "offset": 313,
   "len": 48,
   "en": "\"Or I could @split it up evenly, if you prefer.\"",
   "zh": "「或者在下可將之@split（均分）眾人，悉聽尊便。」",
   "zh_bytes": 39,
   "note": "@split→@均分"
  },
  {
   "offset": 367,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "gath,pool",
   "zh": "匯集,合",
   "zh_bytes": 7,
   "note": "雙觸發詞"
  },
  {
   "offset": 383,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "spli,shar",
   "zh": "均分,分",
   "zh_bytes": 7,
   "note": "keyword 列"
  },
  {
   "offset": 399,
   "len": 18,
   "en": "hut,home,smit,clue",
   "zh": "茅舍,家,史密,線",
   "zh_bytes": 15,
   "note": "clue→線（線索縮略）"
  },
  {
   "offset": 418,
   "len": 45,
   "en": "\"My hut is in the Deep Forest, south of Yew.\"",
   "zh": "「在下茅舍位於尤伊城南之深林中。」",
   "zh_bytes": 34,
   "note": "Yew→尤伊；Deep Forest→深林"
  },
  {
   "offset": 466,
   "len": 29,
   "en": "\"My horse Smith lives there.\"",
   "zh": "「在下之馬史密斯亦居於彼。」",
   "zh_bytes": 28,
   "note": "Smith 馬名音譯"
  },
  {
   "offset": 501,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "job",
   "zh": "職",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "len=3 受限，單字"
  },
  {
   "offset": 505,
   "len": 66,
   "en": "\"I've been a crossbow maker for so long, I've gotten weary of it.\"",
   "zh": "「在下製作弩弓已有年矣，如今已感倦怠。」",
   "zh_bytes": 40,
   "note": "crossbow→弩弓"
  },
  {
   "offset": 573,
   "len": 106,
   "en": "*\"Hopefully, now that my @apprentice has taken over the shop, I'll be able to spend more time as a @bard.\"",
   "zh": "*「所幸今有@apprentice（學徒）接掌店鋪，在下便可多花時光做一名@bard（吟遊詩人）詩人。」",
   "zh_bytes": 61,
   "note": "保留 * 前綴"
  },
  {
   "offset": 685,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "appr,shop,cros",
   "zh": "學徒,店鋪,弩",
   "zh_bytes": 12,
   "note": "keyword 列"
  },
  {
   "offset": 700,
   "len": 55,
   "en": "\"My shop still sells the finest crossbows in the land.\"",
   "zh": "「在下店中所售，仍為全境最精良之弩弓。」",
   "zh_bytes": 40,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 758,
   "len": 88,
   "en": "\"I've done a lot over the years to refine the design, and I trained my apprentice well.\"",
   "zh": "「多年以來在下不斷精進其設計，亦悉心調教學徒。」",
   "zh_bytes": 48,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 849,
   "len": 57,
   "en": "\"I'm sure she'll carry on the tradition in fine fashion.\"",
   "zh": "「在下深信她必能將此技藝傳承得當。」",
   "zh_bytes": 36,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 912,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "bard",
   "zh": "詩人",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword；本句用『詩人』省 byte"
  },
  {
   "offset": 917,
   "len": 40,
   "en": "\"Yes, it's always been a hobby of mine.\"",
   "zh": "「是的，此乃在下一向之雅好。」",
   "zh_bytes": 30,
   "note": "hobby→雅好"
  },
  {
   "offset": 960,
   "len": 68,
   "en": "\"Have you heard the piece 'Stones' that I composed some years ago?\" ",
   "zh": "「閣下可曾聽過在下多年前所譜之曲『石』？」",
   "zh_bytes": 42,
   "note": "'Stones'→曲名『石』"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1034,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "wife,gwen",
   "zh": "妻,葛雯",
   "zh_bytes": 7,
   "note": "Gwenno→葛雯"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1044,
   "len": 76,
   "en": "\"She's had more time to develop her musical talents than I all these years.\"",
   "zh": "「這些年來，她比在下有更多時間鑽研樂藝。」",
   "zh_bytes": 42,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1123,
   "len": 84,
   "en": "\"But after this @quest I hope to join her in @Minoc and enter the artisan's @guild.\"",
   "zh": "「然此次@quest（試煉）之後，在下盼能赴@Minoc（米諾）克與她相聚，加入工匠@guild（公會）。」",
   "zh_bytes": 63,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1213,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "ques",
   "zh": "試煉",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1218,
   "len": 76,
   "en": "\"There always seems to be a quest when you come to visit us, doesn't there?\"",
   "zh": "「閣下每來造訪，似乎總有一場試煉相伴，不是麼？」",
   "zh_bytes": 48,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1297,
   "len": 45,
   "en": "\"Some time you should just drop by for @tea.\"",
   "zh": "「來日閣下也該單純前來品@tea（茶）回。」",
   "zh_bytes": 35,
   "note": "@tea→@茶"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1348,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "tea",
   "zh": "茶",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1352,
   "len": 44,
   "en": "\"All right, make it Frasier's @Folly, then.\"",
   "zh": "「也罷，那就來杯弗雷澤之@Folly（愚醇）吧。」",
   "zh_bytes": 35,
   "note": "Frasier's Folly 酒名"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1402,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "fras,foll",
   "zh": "弗,愚醇",
   "zh_bytes": 7,
   "note": "keyword 列"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1412,
   "len": 47,
   "en": "\"A drink worthy enough to greet an old friend.\"",
   "zh": "「一盞足以款待舊友之佳釀。」",
   "zh_bytes": 28,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1465,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "mino",
   "zh": "米諾",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1470,
   "len": 51,
   "en": "\"Not as big as @Britain, but it's a peaceful town.\"",
   "zh": "「不如@Britain（不列）顛城那般雄偉，卻是個寧靜之鎮。」",
   "zh_bytes": 43,
   "note": "@Britain→@不列顛城"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1527,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "arti,guil,musi",
   "zh": "工匠,公會,樂",
   "zh_bytes": 12,
   "note": "keyword 列"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1542,
   "len": 111,
   "en": "\"Though there is still need for the instruments of war, as I grow in years I would now take up those of peace.\"",
   "zh": "「兵戎之器固仍有所需，然年歲漸長，在下如今更願執持和平之器。」",
   "zh_bytes": 62,
   "note": "對仗『兵戎之器』vs『和平之器』"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1659,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "brit",
   "zh": "不列",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword 截短"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1664,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"You know. Where Mr. @Nose hangs out.\"",
   "zh": "「即@Nose（大鼻）先生平日棲身之所。」",
   "zh_bytes": 29,
   "note": "Mr. Nose→大鼻先生"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1708,
   "len": 12,
   "en": "mr,nose,nibs",
   "zh": "先,鼻,大人",
   "zh_bytes": 10,
   "note": "keyword 列"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1721,
   "len": 54,
   "en": "\"Remember, he doesn't like people to call him that...\"",
   "zh": "「記得，他可不愛旁人這般稱呼……」",
   "zh_bytes": 34,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1781,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "join",
   "zh": "加入",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1786,
   "len": 73,
   "en": "\"I've been with you since we saved you from those @gargoyles, haven't I?\"",
   "zh": "「自吾等將閣下自@gargoyles（魔像族）族手中救出，在下便一路相隨，不是麼？」",
   "zh_bytes": 59,
   "note": "@gargoyles→@魔像族"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1865,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "garg",
   "zh": "魔像",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1870,
   "len": 47,
   "en": "\"They're pretty ugly looking, if you ask me...\"",
   "zh": "「依在下看來，那些傢伙著實醜陋……」",
   "zh_bytes": 36,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1923,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "leav",
   "zh": "離開",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1928,
   "len": 64,
   "en": "\"His nibs, the king, told me I should stay with you constantly.\"",
   "zh": "「那位大人——也就是國王——交代在下須時刻相隨閣下。」",
   "zh_bytes": 54,
   "note": "His nibs→那位大人"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1995,
   "len": 70,
   "en": "\"I'll make an exception when you have to relieve yourself, of course.\"",
   "zh": "「當然啦，閣下要更衣方便之時，在下會破例迴避。」",
   "zh_bytes": 48,
   "note": "relieve→更衣方便"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2071,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "stor",
   "zh": "故事",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2076,
   "len": 77,
   "en": "\"My favorite one is about the time I had to wake Dupre up for a tournament...",
   "zh": "「在下最愛講的，是某次比武大會前喚醒杜普雷的那段往事……",
   "zh_bytes": 56,
   "note": "原文尾無收引號"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2166,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "Dupre cuts in.",
   "zh": "杜普雷插話。",
   "zh_bytes": 12,
   "note": "敘述句"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2181,
   "len": 53,
   "en": "\"Iolo! You promised NEVER to tell anyone about that!\"",
   "zh": "「尤洛！你發誓過此事絕不外傳的！」",
   "zh_bytes": 34,
   "note": "Dupre 對 Iolo 喊話"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2241,
   "len": 90,
   "en": "\"Yes, you're right. I'm sorry.\" He whispers to you, \"Ask me later when he's not around...\"",
   "zh": "「是的，你說得對，抱歉。」他低聲對閣下道：「待他不在時再來問在下……」",
   "zh_bytes": 70,
   "note": "兩段對話拼接"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2336,
   "len": 72,
   "en": "\"But maybe I shouldn't tell you about that. After all, I did promise...\"",
   "zh": "「不過此事或許還是不該告訴閣下，畢竟在下確實許下了承諾……」",
   "zh_bytes": 60,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2415,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "bye",
   "zh": "別",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "len=3 受限"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2419,
   "len": 63,
   "en": "\"I've still got to tell you that story about Dupre sometime...\"",
   "zh": "「終有一日，在下還是要把杜普雷那段故事說與閣下聽……」",
   "zh_bytes": 54,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2485,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "spam",
   "zh": "罐肉",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "Monty Python Spam 梗"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2490,
   "len": 25,
   "en": "\"Ask Shamino about that.\"",
   "zh": "「此事去問夏米諾吧。」",
   "zh_bytes": 22,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2532,
   "len": 6,
   "en": "humbug",
   "zh": "騙術",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "Dickens 梗"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2559,
   "len": 25,
   "en": "\"Ask Shamino about that.\"",
   "zh": "「此事去問夏米諾吧。」",
   "zh_bytes": 22,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2592,
   "len": 25,
   "en": "\"Ask Shamino about that.\"",
   "zh": "「此事去問夏米諾吧。」",
   "zh_bytes": 22,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2624,
   "len": 2,
   "en": "yn",
   "zh": "yn",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "yes/no token"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2629,
   "len": 66,
   "en": "\"Oh, you should get my wife @Gwenno to teach it to you some time.\"",
   "zh": "「噢，閣下他日該請在下之妻@Gwenno（葛雯）教你一曲。」",
   "zh_bytes": 43,
   "note": "@Gwenno→@葛雯"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2702,
   "len": 27,
   "en": "\"It's one of my favorites.\"",
   "zh": "「此乃在下心愛之曲。」",
   "zh_bytes": 22,
   "note": ""
  },
